text: They Paid With Their Blood () is a 1955 Turkish drama film directed by Osman F. Seden. It stars Esref Kolçak, Neriman Köksal, Kenan Pars, Talat Artemel, Mualla Kaynak, Kadir Savun and Tamer Balci. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1955 films Category:Turkish films Category:Turkish drama films Category:1955 drama films
